00:26:38,976 --> 00:26:41,879
They've really caused massive disruption

456
00:26:42,240 --> 00:26:43,841
to the strategies of these guys.

457
00:26:45,755 --> 00:26:48,479
And I mean, this is basically peer pressure 101, right?

458
00:26:49,179 --> 00:26:52,203
If you say, I'm not going to be a part of this, and then that

