00:50:29,517 --> 00:50:34,178
Yeah, that's something that I definitely want to try out. I think for a couple of reasons.

882
00:50:34,598 --> 00:50:38,539
One, for the randomness factor, but it also means that people will have to be...

883
00:50:39,179 --> 00:50:42,620
when they're devising their tactics, they're going to have to build in fail-safes.

884
00:50:42,840 --> 00:50:45,841
So, I mean, the very simple idea I had was, you know, we could make it a coin,

885
00:50:45,921 --> 00:50:48,382
make it 50-50 whether a hit lands or not.

